{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2076, "height": 2812, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [151, 731, 232, 1452], "block_id": 0, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "doc_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏人物", "block_bbox": [883, 244, 1324, 310], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "始祖一世流芳公：相传，杜姓当明洪武初，自山西洪桐迁居渑池坻坞西村，号“破锅杜氏”。意者，方迁之时，兄弟离散，恐不能相顾，故碎一铁锅，各执一片，以作记认欤。杜氏当明时本有旧谱，至明末屡遭变乱，旧谱因之而失，始祖之名讳、配偶遂不可考。曰流芳者，乃后人追称之辞也。\n", "block_bbox": [334, 406, 1858, 669], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二世杜忠：流芳公长子，字良臣，东门之祖。", "block_bbox": [426, 692, 1205, 740], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二世杜孝：流芳公次子，字德顺，西门之祖。", "block_bbox": [429, 764, 1207, 812], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜宣：旧谱未载，不知世次，亦不知所出、所传。按：时代似早于四世祖真金。其人载于《渑池县志》，为明代永乐二十一年(1423）举人，曾任光禄寺丞（光禄寺的属官，从六品，禄96石）。\n", "block_bbox": [340, 834, 1861, 1029], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "四世杜真金：田宅甚广，蓄资甚厚，邑称巨富。明万历时，天子诏养义马，敕赐“义民”，葬西坟。据墓碑，公号临泉，明嘉靖二十年(1541)生，万历四十七年(1619)逝世，享年七十八岁。\n", "block_bbox": [341, 1051, 1862, 1243], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "五世杜三光：明代陕西瓦云驿丞，迁居窑湾，为东门一派之祖。据墓碑，公号少泉，逝世于崇祯陆年(1633)，因碑缺字，致生年不明，碑上有“拾年”等字，而崇祯前之光宗、熹宗在位均未满十年，神宗（万历帝)在位达48年。再向前推，穆宗在位也只6年，世宗（嘉靖帝）在位44年。据此，可大致推定三光公生于万历或嘉靖年间，其可能的生年有嘉靖四十年（1561）、万历十年（1582）、万历二十年（1592）共三个，具体且待后人考证。\n", "block_bbox": [341, 1267, 1865, 1670], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "—以下杜氏人物按村列举如下。", "block_bbox": [436, 1764, 1076, 1814], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "上西村前街北坻坞上阙：", "block_bbox": [349, 1836, 813, 1885], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "九世杜允惠：乡耆，公秉性刚直、慷慨好施，受恩皇家，可法可式。公积资建祖祠，基址已定而殁。长子廷用克承厥志而终其事焉。\n", "block_bbox": [343, 1906, 1867, 2028], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "九世杜允举：监生。", "block_bbox": [347, 2049, 710, 2098], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "九世杜允炳：属温庄门，监生。", "block_bbox": [346, 2119, 908, 2170], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十世杜廷焕：属温庄门，监生。", "block_bbox": [347, 2190, 909, 2240], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十世杜廷用：允惠子，监生，公继父志，创建祖祠，其为人端方、正直，乡邻仰德欤。", "block_bbox": [344, 2259, 1820, 2311], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十世杜廷行：允举子，布政司经历。", "block_bbox": [347, 2332, 993, 2382], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十世杜廷选：湖北典史。", "block_bbox": [347, 2404, 797, 2452], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一世杜林魁：廷行长子，武生。", "block_bbox": [348, 2474, 950, 2523], "block_id": 17, "block_order": 17}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9583595395088196, "coordinate": [341.1461181640625, 1267.23681640625, 1865.5023193359375, 1670.193359375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9520120024681091, "coordinate": [334.84808349609375, 406.45660400390625, 1858.208984375, 669.1351928710938]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9285843372344971, "coordinate": [341.5123291015625, 1051.0257568359375, 1862.1605224609375, 1243.7159423828125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9230237603187561, "coordinate": [340.6505126953125, 834.886352539062